### Service Dependencies - Test Endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check (shows all service connections)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 1b. Health Check with App Prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/health

### 2. Create User (uses DB + Cache)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Smith"
}

### 3. Get User (first call - from DB, then cached)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/123

### 4. Get User Again (should come from cache)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/123

### 5. Create Order (uses OrderService → UserService → DB + Cache)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "123",
  "product": "Laptop",
  "amount": 1299.99
}

### 6. Get Order
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/order-1234567890

### 7. Create Multiple Orders (demonstrates service reuse)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "456",
  "product": "Mouse",
  "amount": 29.99
}

